        <mxCell id="52aDZY7gCkw2FH3TF3l5-91" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Notes van states&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;- Belangrijk dat ALLE iElement afgeleiden de Accept functie overschijft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;- Alle state implementeren de IElement interface, en de abstracte `State` classe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;- States krijgen de builder pattarn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Alle visiters naar elements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1" vertex="1">
